        "captions": "[{\"start\": 0, \"end\": 8280000, \"text\": \"出国住酒店要用品的5句实用英语\\n收藏这 5 句，覆盖索要不同客房用品的全高频场景\\n1. Can I have a pair of slippers?\\n2. Can I get a toothbrush set?\\n3. May I have two more bath towels?\\n4. Can I get some extra bottled water?\\n5. Do you have a travel adapter I can borrow?\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 8280000, \"end\": 13752000, \"text\": \"Can I have a pair of slippers?\\n能给我一双拖鞋吗？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 13752000, \"end\": 18408000, \"text\": \"Can I get a toothbrush set?\\n能给我一套牙具吗？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 18408000, \"end\": 24672000, \"text\": \"May I have two more bath towels?\\n能再给我两条浴巾吗？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 24672000, \"end\": 30936000, \"text\": \"Can I get some extra bottled water?\\n能多给我几瓶矿泉水吗？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 30936000, \"end\": 38400000, \"text\": \"Do you have a travel adapter I can borrow?\\n你们有可以借的旅行转换插头吗？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 38400000, \"end\": 41448000, \"text\": \"你住酒店最常向前台要什么用品呀？\", \"font_size\": 10}]",
